Burp suit:- is a tool used to find vulnerabilities in web applications and now is also used in testing mobile applications and API testing
        3 Editions are available so far 1) Burp Suite Enterprise Edition
                                        2) Burp suite professional 
                                        3) Burp Suite Community Edition
  it can be installed in all OS but you gotta make sure that the device has available java run time environment.


Sublist3r :- is used for finding subdomain of targeting domain.
    COMMAND:- sublist3r -d tatget.com (-d stands for domain)

ffuf :- its web fuzzing tool used for fuzzing
  COMMAND :- ffuf -u https:// target.com /fuff -w weblist.com 

